      "title": "4 crore ice is caught from the estate",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A suspect who transported a stock of ice drug worth nearly 4 crore rupees from Mannar in a luxury car has been arrested by the Special Task Force in Wattala area.",
        "4 kg of ice drug, 320 grams, was found in the possession of the suspect.",
        "The suspect had carefully packed the ice drug in 1 kg packets and hidden it in the car."
      ],
